{"tid":2164880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每一日公佈確診人數減少, 推遲選舉既理據又柒左一大截","createTime":"2020-08-19T12:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T12:52:24.000Z","uid":195193,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6db4d0cf6f75a1283643e8429fdf3a534abef208","tid":2164880,"uid":195193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:40:22.000Z","msg":"明明係驚輸, 講到大條道理照顧市民健康<br />\nDQ完又要提請人大又延期依樣個樣<br />\n其實條街一樣係咁多人<br />\n一樣有咁多人要出門返工<br />\n<br />\n爆個九號風一落風球, 黨鐵同巴士站又係迫爆人<br />\n只係一日既活動你推遲足一年<br />\n九月頭確診數如果得返個位數甚至更少既話<br />\n鄭柒婆依個決定就更加仆街<br />\n<br />\n大家繼續努力抗疫<br />\n唔係等下星期五佢迫班泛民決定去留<br />\n係等確診數繼續跌<br />\n然後大大聲鬧爆佢<br />\n<br />\n黃碧雲仆街啲定係鄭柒婆仆街啲<br />\n唔洗講出口啦係咪呀"},{"pid":"959825f1873ef37ebb829fb24902da54d9672a1e","tid":2164880,"uid":195193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:41:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"09f57461b5a779fe0f2d12da8d4d7ae7d1261563","tid":2164880,"uid":195193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:43:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7040e71e5815ac87d3a456d48f8e735a72189d21","tid":2164880,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:44:36.000Z","msg":"用法律去打壓手足同支持國安法<br />\n支持江樂士做下一批美國制裁人選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/aaronMCN/status/1295929570256998401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FaaronMCN%2Fstatus%2F1295929570256998401&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=3c0a87ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FaaronMCN%2Fstatus%2F1295929570256998401&h=cea44966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/aaronMCN/status/1295929570256998401</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5XmBzvQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5XmBzvQ.jpg&h=eac5eb83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3a33119e98a6eb6b157c1de99f695e9efecb68c","tid":2164880,"uid":